{
  "stem": "5639.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were-- there were three girls who worked with me, two other girls who worked with me in the cutting room.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was my suggestion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was equally taken up by them, except that I am in Australia, and I didn't have the survivors here, and the one in Israel has the largest amount of survivors from Bedzin.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not everybody was willing to give a testimony in his favor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they said he took bribes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course he took bribes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What-- he needed the bribes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He supported the Jewish Resistance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the closure in the ghetto--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the 1st of August, 1943.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't a closure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a total extermination of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A total deportation.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it happened from-- in the night of between Saturday and Sunday, at the time when our watchfulness was relaxed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In our naivete, we thought, why should they disturb their own Sunday in order to surround us, and to conduct a action of extermination?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They have us all the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And only quite recently, it dawned on me, that they had us in ghetto, but they didn't have us concentrated in our place of work.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were the masses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were the numbers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And from there, they could expect a resistance. 2,000 men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But on Saturday, from Saturday to Sunday, everybody went to the families.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One lived here, one lived there, or one lived somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the need of normalization in people living in dangerous situation is enormous.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Rossner must have had an inkling, is-- something is happening.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember when he told me-- must have been winter, '42.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now I know it was winter '42, that the Germans finally reached the Final Solution, Endlosung.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Final Solution in German is Endlosung.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I thought, terrific.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
